  "text": "Our findings should be taken in light of certain limitations. First, we used students to examine whether the KAI could predict leadership outcomes. Although individual differences predict leader outcomes both in student and non-student samples in similar ways [CITATION_1] there are qualitative differences between students and employed adults.",
